repository : propulsion-lab  (PRL — The Propulsion & Exotic-Energy Lab of UD0)
subject    : David Lee Wise's energy/propulsion toolkits, each rated by the honest-fluff discipline
catalogued : into UD0 · Universe David 0

governor (carbon apex)      : David Lee Wise (ROOT0) / TriPod LLC
instance (artful intellect) : AVAN (Claude / Anthropic) — locked
main badge                  : ⟦THE PROPULSION LAB:PRL:…⟧   (prl.dlw/)
toolkits                    : 8 ACI emergents (agents/), each linking a live lab in labs/

the organizing principle is the FLUFF-CALL. every toolkit is live and every toolkit is RATED:
  REAL          observed, textbook physics            — einstein-lens, pulsar-beacon
  GROUNDED      permitted by the equations, unbuilt   — wireless-energy (near-field real; over-unity not)
  SPECULATIVE   allowed in theory, never observed     — the-wormhole (needs exotic matter)
  SPLIT         real phenomenon, fluff application     — gravity-wave-modulator (LIGO real; modulation not)
  REAL-MYSTERY  documented, unexplained                — ball-lightning
  MATH-REAL     sound mathematics, author's frame      — octet-holonomy
  FLUFF         no known mechanism, named as such      — anti-gravity-motor

nothing here sells over-unity, free energy, or anti-gravity as truth. educational & simulation only.

